We are enjoying catching up with all of the episodes of Modern Family.  The acting is wonderful everyone has such perfect comedic timing...even the younger actors!  I love this show!  I look forward to seeing the kids grown and how the adults cope with getting older!  Its a laugh-out-loud experience!  This show makes my day.  We love it!  All of the Seasons are great fun to watch!  Original!

My husband and I (81 and 62 years old) love this show! We are up to season 4 and every one we've watched is very funny, entertaining, and a light, delightful break from the trials and tribulations of daily living. It has close captioning for the hard of hearing and a variety of languages. There is such a wonderful mix of characters, and the writing is solid. A little more mixture of races would be appreciated.
